<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><?workdir /C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\temp\references\sql_grammar\topics?><?path2project ..\..\?><topic xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="references_sql_where" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.2" domains="(topic hi-d)                             (topic ut-d)                             (topic indexing-d)                            (topic hazard-d)                            (topic abbrev-d)                            (topic pr-d)                             (topic sw-d)                            (topic ui-d)    " class="- topic/topic " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="topic:1">
  <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="title:1">sql where</title>
  <body class="- topic/body " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="body:1">
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="section:1"><title class="- topic/title " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="title:2">where 语句</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="p:1">用于规定选择的标准。</p>
    </section>
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="section:2"><title class="- topic/title " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="title:3">语法</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="p:2"><codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1">where field1_name &lt;运算符&gt; value1 [and|or &lt;another condition&gt;...]</codeblock></p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="p:3">&lt;cs_name&gt;：集合空间名</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="p:4">&lt;cl_name&gt;：集合名</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="p:5">&lt;运算符&gt;：现在可用的运算符包括：&lt;(小于)，&gt;(大于)，&lt;=(小于等于)，&gt;=(大于等于)，&lt;&gt;(不等于)，=(等于)</p>
    </section>
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="section:3"><title class="- topic/title " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="title:4">示例</title>
      <ul class="- topic/ul " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="ul:1">
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="li:1"><p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="p:6">如果希望选取age&gt;10的记录，可以在select语句添加where子句：</p>
          <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="p:7"><codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="codeblock:2">db.exec("select * from foo.bar where age&gt;10") </codeblock></p>
        </li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="li:2">如果希望删除age&gt;10的记录，也可以在delete语句中添加where子句：
          <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="C:\SequoiaDB\doc\references\sql_grammar\topics\where.dita" xtrc="codeblock:3">db.execUpdate("delete from foo.bar where age&gt;10")</codeblock>
          当然同样能在update语句中添加where子句。</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </body>
